blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Enteleo Entei and Solgaleo fusion Fire/Psychic Type Ability: Full Metal Body/Flame Body Stats: HP - 140, Atk - 145, Def - 105,...
caption:
Enteleo

Entei and Solgaleo fusion

Fire/Psychic Type

Ability: Full Metal Body/Flame Body

Stats: HP - 140, Atk - 145, Def - 105, SpA - 120, SpD - 90, Spe - 105

Signature move: Solar Blast - Drawing its power from the sun, it blasts its opponent with a blast of hot energy.  Power - 150, Accuracy - 100. Needs a turn to charge.  Charges instantly in the sun. 

The Solar God Pokemon

Enteleo is the god of the sun and all things fiery.  Its body spews out cosmic energy.  It draws its power from the sun and will use the sun’s solar flares for a devastating attack.

Request for @inkydragons. I hope you like it!
